endlich erzeugte 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

-Algebra
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

.
 Es ist:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Gamma(X)\text{ irreduzibel }\Leftrightarrow I(X)=\rad I(X).
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

